{"tid":100361,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真post]究竟連登邊個台最多靚仔。","createTime":"2017-01-30T03:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T03:33:53.000Z","uid":23170,"like":11,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c3717cfcf6611408e2b84cc2bc9f9ffb3033471","tid":100361,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:15:01.000Z","msg":"咁做其實因為我發現其實好多連登仔都其實幾靚仔，特別係cd-rom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申，最柒係樓主本人，拉低哂感情台啲質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家都知<strong>波台</strong>多痴線佬同中年肥腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依個一定可以skip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>學術校園</strong>多數都係中學雞，嫩得黎但係未發育完成唔洗客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，間唔中見到啲ive或者大學靚仔囉最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>政事同時事台</strong>一定全部都係毒樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其是熱狗同青政狗兩者都一定0靚仔，其他真心討論時事一定都近3或者過3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>娛樂台</strong>應該都有少少靚仔，嗰堆瘋狂喺娛樂台出post通常都係靚仔記者打手為左搵返飲食先黎依啲毒撚討論區。不過唔出post長期留連喺娛樂台應該係女人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>動漫台</strong> .........唔洗講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>遊戲台apps台</strong>應該幾多靚仔直仔（估計大部分都有女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )。但醜都應該佔半數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>影視台</strong>應該好多都肥柒柒。因為日日夜夜都煲戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>講故台</strong>一定好多文青。不過以往好多文學作家都係醜樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唯有少數寫細膩啲嘅短篇應該先係靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>潮流台</strong>。一定係成班死毒撚樣已經無得救嘅地步先要用衫搭救。實醜樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>上班台</strong>嗰度一定好多2中間嘅成熟哥哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>財經台</strong>。有幾多財經人士真係靚仔呀。李超仁已經係一個活活生嘅代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>飲食台</strong>。多數識煮嘢食都有魅力搭救。應該幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>旅遊台</strong>。會寫遊記又有人陪一定係靚仔加少少mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗起都扯扯地<br />\n<br />\n<strong>汽車台</strong>。未入過。唔知。不過有得車都應該係筍盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>音樂台</strong>。識唱歌有幾多真係靚仔呀。靚仔又唔會識唱歌。eg. 香港樂壇。不過一定都有啲唔識唱歌或者任何樂器嘅靚仔都硬要上音樂台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>硬件台</strong>。識整電腦一定係毒撚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>攝影台</strong>。影風景相雖然成春日唔上鏡。不過有小部份都係靚仔嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係大多數都係醜樣搞到自己懶係鬼佬feel咁。一句講哂。。嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>玩具台</strong>。我一直都唔知有依個台存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩figure一定唔靚仔，詳情參考動漫台<br />\n<br />\n<strong>寵物台</strong>。有寵物嘅男仔通常又有愛心又靚仔。多數都有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過一定係靚仔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>軟件台</strong>，同硬件台差唔多道埋㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>活動台</strong>。 約出黎通常都5pmk, 但係靚仔嘅5pmk都會死上香討，唔靚仔嘅咪淪落喺連登識其他醜樣囉<br />\n<br />\n<strong>直播台</strong>，聽過個男仔聲。。幾好j, 不過好j嘅聲應該唔靚仔，eg. 雲海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>站務台</strong>，廢台，不過admin應該幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>成人台</strong>，成堆雞蟲，有女仲洗上咩。。可以唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>感情台</strong>。。1234bb幾靚仔呀，約過啲都有幾多好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>創意台</strong>多數膠底。。但係都有啲靚仔大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550eef28e1e655a67e3d890cdaf4847382e2512e","tid":100361,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:15:17.000Z","msg":"summary...<br />\n各台靚仔佔比率 [由高至低]<br />\n旅遊台（90%)<br />\n寵物台（80%)<br />\n創意台（75%)<br />\n飲食台（60%)<br />\n汽車台（60%)<br />\n感情台（50%)<br />\n遊戲台apps台（50%)<br />\n上班台（40%)<br />\n講故台（25%)<br />\n學術校園台（20%)<br />\n音樂台（15%)<br />\n娛樂台（10%)<br />\n波台（5%)<br />\n攝影台（5%)<br />\n潮流台（3%)<br />\ncc政事台（1%)<br />\n直播台（1%)<br />\n財經台（0.1%)<br />\n玩具台（0.01%)<br />\n硬件台（0%)<br />\n影視台（0%)<br />\n軟件台（0%)<br />\n活動台（0%)<br />\n動漫台（-100%)<br />\n成人台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb67cb235134a9c39d0ca9187667073272dc671","tid":100361,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:15:37.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d011c47f9674580880c7adc2a8c9bfec3808e51","tid":100361,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"0a57206f16a2fef0d532d5d7dd5edc87fc9fe703","tid":100361,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:21:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/JerryC.Official/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FJerryC.Official%2F&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2Fb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=bd39905a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/JerryC.Official/</a><br />\n<br />\n點睇呢條友?"},{"pid":"7ec3d1e2a75ce8996bb0901b604cdc5d7dabe406","tid":100361,"uid":31429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:22:27.000Z","msg":"吹水台"},{"pid":"7ca9b699968e875fbd9895d32dc45eed8d040049","tid":100361,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:24:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acf2a38ae3424aecaaf2f114bd341511d12ace80","tid":100361,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0